Class ComparableObjectItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jfree.data.ComparableObjectItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OHLCItem, VectorDataItem, XIntervalDataItem, XYIntervalDataItem, YIntervalDataItem

    public class ComparableObjectItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable
    Represents one (Comparable, Object) data item for use in a ComparableObjectSeries.
    Since:
    1.0.3
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
